{"title":"《瘦马记》人物诗画","authors":["王进修　徐启雄"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":9,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"《瘦马记》人物诗画\t王进修诗　徐启雄画\t韩　芒　种"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瘦马、穷队、贫农，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"废寝忘食为公。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只因决心乘东风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸡毛飞上天空！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依靠党和群众，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打退邪气进攻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社栋梁气如虹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人称赞芒种。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青松不怕风霜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄正在成长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习毛泽东思想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党性百倍加强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韩芒种"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长　水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抬石槽，上河工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带头和社员一起劳动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有团结，有批评，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟社员亲如家人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对富裕中农，心中有数，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对保守思想，也能顶住。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里马，只有伯乐能相；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从无到有，唯我公社能养。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勤俭建国，自力更生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚持政策，决心革命。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是好当家，立场坚定，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱贫下中农的贴心人。\t  长　水\t李　十　三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也为集体，也爱社，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是脑袋有点保守。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不抽他烟，不喝他酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可还是轻信了梁斗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要看得远，识得透，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老经验已经不够。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李十三\t梁　斗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘴甜心里黑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马料当猪食。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁斗有个原则："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水过地皮湿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真刀对真枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级对阶级，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两条道路斗争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"展开在饲养室。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你挖社会主义墙脚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们挖复辟的基石。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"借你这反面教员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"揭露资本主义实质。\t   梁　斗（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}